In the above formulas
\begin{eqnarray}
R(m_X)=\frac{m_X}{m_\chi},~P_j=1+R(m_j)^2-\frac{1}{2}(R(m_X)^2+R(m_Y)^2),
~G_i=\frac{\Gamma_i m_i}{m_\chi^2}
\end{eqnarray}
